    <item>
      <title>Le Pen爆炸了“政治”裁决，该裁决禁止法国选举出价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/le-pen-blasts-political-ruling-that-bars-french-election-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国极右翼领导人马林·勒庞（Marine Le Pen）决定禁止她竞选当选的办公室五年，并说这有效地从2027年的总统竞选中淘汰了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/le-pen-blasts-political-ruling-that-bars-french-election-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 18:36:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金签证改造的诱惑富裕到新西兰作为避风港</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/golden-visa-revamp-tempts-wealthy-to-eye-new-zealand-as-haven</link>
      <description><![CDATA[移民部长埃里卡·斯坦福（Erica Stanford）说，随着地缘政治紧张局势的上升促使富人考虑国外的选择，新西兰正在对其对美国和欧洲进行改造的黄金签证计划的“红热”兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/golden-visa-revamp-tempts-wealthy-to-eye-new-zealand-as-haven</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
